{
  "stem": "2916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if I'm separated from her, I'll never see her again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course in truth, in probably less than an hour she was already not alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we were marching off to the right, Mengele said to me, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I'm 13.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, from now on, remember you are 16.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I knew that 16 meant that I was allowed to stay among the grownups.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew that probably there will be other selections when I will have to lie about my age.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were marching towards the camp Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were marching for a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we came to that famous gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By now, most people know it, metal-- black metal gate and above it the words, [NON-ENGLISH], which in English means work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what they meant by it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother said, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means that we will work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we will get proper treatment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what they mean by free, but we'll be treated properly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we arrived into the camp, the gates opened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know to how much detail I can go at this point, so please you tell me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were taken to the showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other things I would have mentioned along the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just, perhaps, I'll mention that the camp was surrounded by high wire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later, we found out that the wire was electrified.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so these were the electrified fences that many people later on who decided to commit suicide would just walk to the fence and touch it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And instantly, they were killed, electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that in Auschwitz the expression, I'm going to walk to the fence, meant, goodbye, I'm committing suicide.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
